{
  "stem": "4570.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, my hair was very light blonde, and-- and I have blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, I mean, people thought, you know, a Jew is somebody with big nose and black hair.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father didn't look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was, I think, deported on the 19th-- 10-- 9-- no, that was the date-- I-- I do not know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He must have gone in-- in '41 to Terezin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was deported from-- from Terezin to Treblinka on the 19th-- 10th-- 1942, and murdered.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that-- this is the last.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think that most of those dates that they have in the archives are not very correct.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother is working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was distraught when he left his job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He loved his job, because-- also, that he wasn't all the time at home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had sort of a-- a much more interesting life, traveling and coming back home again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he aged when he lost his job, even, you know, before the Germans came, before all that happened.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He-- he became, all at once, a very old man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My job in the bank?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was real fun.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I applied for the job, I-- at that time, it was very fashionable to have cocoa-colored nail polish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went to the bank manager who had that ad in the-- in the paper.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and he was a Viennese-- a very charming man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was so amused by that 16-year-old with the cocoa-colored fingernails, that he gave me the job.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, but you know, when you come, you better take the nail polish off.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't think it-- it would come over very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was in the first floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And downstairs was a normal bank.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
